ctrl-a d : detach
screen -r : reattach to existing session

SPLITS
ctrl-a S : split horizontal
ctrl-a | : split vertical
ctrl-a TAB : change focus to other regions when split
ctrl-a Q : close all regions except current(?) (inactive ones)
ctrl-a X : close the currently focused region

ctrl-a :resize max : open screen command line and resize to max
	30% 
	increase/decrease with +n -n,
	set to specific size with n,
	set all to equal with -b
